text: "The Last Song" is a 1992 song by Elton John and is the third single from his 23rd studio album The One. It went to number 7 in Canada, number 21 in the United Kingdom, number 23 in the United States, number 27 in New Zealand, number 28 in Ireland and number 32 in Australia.
